name: Flaming Eye Concept - LORA
description:
Trained on nai.
Good results with 0.9-1 weigths.
Prompt activator : color flaming eye, color eye trail, flaming eye, eye trail
Negative prompt : animal ears, horse girl

You can change the color ! It can do either eye trail or flaming eye but to optmize success rate, i put them both.
This is a gacha lora, success rate :
- without other loras = 8/10
- with other loras = 4/10 (decreasing with other lora's weight)

Sometimes you will need negative prompt (animal ears, horse girl, horse ears) because a lot of pictures in dataset are from Uma Musume Pretty Derby (Horse girl racing) lol

Reviews are really appreciated, i love to see the community use my work, that's why I share it.
If you like my work, you can tip me here.

Got a specific request ? I'm open for commission on my fiverr gig *! If you provide enough data, OCs are accepted

*Any paid request will not be presented on this page, unless you give me permission to.
